name: DIRT GANG
description:
(MENS)

Dirt Gang Shirt features a multi-color print of various Dirt Label Designs, which are tattoo over the arms. The back features DIRT PUNK CLUB RULES for the Club. This shirt also features the "Dirt Label" by John St. John emblem printed on the side of the left sleeve. This Garment is made of 100% fine soft ring-spun cotton. (DISTRESS NECK, SLEEVES TO CREATE A CUSTOM LOOK). This shirt is available in black.

name: DIRT PUNK CLUB
description: Dirt Punk Club shirt features a multi-color print on both the front and back, embedded with OVER 300 hand set swarovski crystals. This shirt also features the “Dirt Label” by John St. John emblem printed on the side of the left sleeve. This garment is made of 100% fine ring-spun combed cotton. This light weight fine jersey knit shirt is exceptionally smooth and tight knit making it just as opaque as a much heavier fabric. This shirt is available in Red Acid Wash & Black.
